Package: python3-otpgui
Architecture: all
Suggests: sops
Depends: python3-gi, python3-pyotp, python3-yaml, python3:any, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, hicolor-icon-theme, python3-pkg-resources, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Provides an OTP generator compatible with totp.
 The package python3-otpgui provides a graphical application that display
 TOTP codes for two-factor-authentication (2FA). Secrets to generate codes
 are stored in a YAML file (optionally encrypted by sops)
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.
